node.text: I don’t care who you voted for or what party you belong to, I care about solutions and this video feels like a much better strategy to keep my family and country safe rather than the current strategy. To me it doesn’t matter whether this message came from a gay liberal or homophobic conservative… It still wouldn’t change my support for the strategy. We have to stop allowing ourselves to become so easily divided which in turn prevents us from developing solutions together. This is also a glimpse of what leadership should look like. @jockowillink preaches and lives the idea of accountability for our own actions and this is an absolutely breathtaking example of how our Commander In Chief should behave, all of them, from any party 🇺🇸 @jockowillink @hodgetwins

node.title: Detach yourself from political parties and attach yourself to solutions

node.text: I don’t care who you voted for or what party you belong to, I care about solutions and this video feels like a much better strategy to keep my family and country safe rather than the current strategy. To me it doesn’t matter whether this message came from a gay liberal or homophobic conservative… It still wouldn’t change my support for the strategy. We have to stop allowing ourselves to become so easily divided which in turn prevents us from developing solutions together. This is also a glimpse of what leadership should look like. @jockowillink preaches and lives the idea of accountability for our own actions and this is an absolutely breathtaking example of how our Commander In Chief should behave, all of them, from any party 🇺🇸 @jockowillink @hodgetwins

node.text: The kids wanted to go camping one last time before school starts so we loaded up and took the loooong 30 second trip up to the teepee in our backyard. They insisted on sleeping in hammocks instead of the usual rooftop tent on our Polaris Ranger. Astonishingly they stayed in their hammocks all night instead of trying to pile in the tent at 3am 😅 I even slept in a hammock and it was quite enjoyable 😴 (ps with the insanely high wildfire danger right now I feel the need to mention that our fire was from a self contained gas fire pit…not a wood burning campfire 🔥🏕)
